Dialogue: 9,0:04:26.91,0:04:32.12,SAO1,,0,0,0,,{There's nothing more boring than watching others play an RPG from the sidelines.}Chẳng có gì nhàm chán hơn là phải ngồi xem người chơi khác chơi game nhập vai.{I beg to differ.}{as I commented earlier... isn't that what we're doing?}{well, kayaba couldn't filter out all the boring stuff like the anime does for us... right?}
